1. Dependencies
	OpenCV 2, libjsoncpp

2. Compilation (for example)
    g++ -lopencv_core -lopencv_highgui -lopencv_imgproc -lopencv_photo -lopencv_video -ljsoncpp -stdc++11 -pthread main.cpp camera.cpp motiontrack.cpp hardware.cpp
3. Problems
    In the case the camera fails to load check that you have the correct kernel module installed and loaded.
